{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"bddbef27-e3ba-42c0-9870-f528209d930e","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, and tasks.md under specrunner/changes/claude-adapter-write-scope/ on branch change/claude-adapter-write-scope-96a1868f. design.md covers Context/Goals/Decisions (D1–D6: SDK native sandbox scoping step-agent writes to cwd, fail-open via failIfUnavailable:false with a single stderr warning, reads unrestricted, Bash preserved, one-shot+codex untouched)/Risks/Open Questions. spec.md has 3 requirements (workspace write scope, fail-open-warn-once, one-shot unchanged) with 6 scenarios and SHALL/MUST keywords. tasks.md has T-01..T-06 with acceptance criteria, TC-SB-01..05 test plan mirroring TC-AR-01. No source edits (planning only); no ADR path references.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-07-09T03:50:51.839Z","endedAt":"2026-07-09T04:00:09.871Z"}
